{
  "page_id": "4918261390",
  "title": "How to generate sailhyp.elf with local *.dts",
  "version": 7,
  "url": "/spaces/CARSFW/pages/4918261390/How+to+generate+sailhyp.elf+with+local+.dts",
  "last_modified": "2024-11-21T06:47:56.000+01:00",
  "last_modified_by": "LIU Dezhi (XC-CP/ESW2-CN)",
  "parent_id": "4916777106",
  "children": [],
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Qualcomm don't release hypervisor source code to us. We can only modify limited configurations of hypervisor by *.dts."
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "/confluence/download/attachments/4918261390/make%20sailhypdts.png?version=1&modificationDate=1729825070000&api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/How to generate sailhyp.elf with local _.dts/make sailhypdts.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The currently released versions of sailhyp_nosym.elf are for single-core, and the multi-core versions still need to be released by Qualcomm in the future."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "1. Prepareration"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Please make sure you can build and generate autosarsailbaremetal.elf refer to How to setup QC SAIL build environment"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "2. generate sailhyp.elf"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Take r00010.1 ES08 for example, because it can find autosar version sailhyp_nosym.elf since the ES08."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "2.1. download sailhyp_nosym.elf"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Download sailhyp_nosym.elf from snapdragon-auto-hqx-4-5-6-0_test_device_autosar /sail_autosar / sail_proc  /build / ms / bin  /SAIL_CASAR / DEBUG / lemans"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "https://chipcode.qti.qualcomm.com/robert-bosch-gmbh/snapdragon-auto-hqx-4-5-6-0_test_device_autosar/tree/r00010.1"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/How%20to%20generate%20sailhyp.elf%20with%20local%20*.dts/image-2024-10-25_10-38-49.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/How to generate sailhyp.elf with local _.dts/image-2024-10-25_10-38-49.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "2.2. copy sailhyp_nosym.elf"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Copy sailhyp_nosym.elf to  sail_autosar\\sail_proc\\build\\ms\\bin\\SAIL_CASAR\\DEBUG\\lemans"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "2.3. modify  lemansau-sailhyp-autosar.dts"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Modify dts as your requirement. dts located in sail_autosar/sail_proc/BSP/scripts/lemansau-sailhyp-autosar.dts"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "2.4. generate sailhyp.elf"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "ES06 and ES08 makefile script is different, please follow as below."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "ES08 Project （r00010.1 ES08）:"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/How%20to%20generate%20sailhyp.elf%20with%20local%20*.dts/image-2024-10-25_10-46-31.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/How to generate sailhyp.elf with local _.dts/image-2024-10-25_10-46-31.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "ES06 Project （r00008.1 ES06）:"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/How%20to%20generate%20sailhyp.elf%20with%20local%20*.dts/image-2024-11-21_13-5-51.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/How to generate sailhyp.elf with local _.dts/image-2024-11-21_13-5-51.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "After finish, sailhyp.elf will generate"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/How%20to%20generate%20sailhyp.elf%20with%20local%20*.dts/image-2024-10-25_10-49-23.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/How to generate sailhyp.elf with local _.dts/image-2024-10-25_10-49-23.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "we should use signed/sailhyp.elf"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "attachments："
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "given by Case 07529936"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "multi-core sailhyp_nosym.elf : sailhyp_nosym.elf"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "multi-core  DTS                      : lemansau-sailhyp-autosar.dts.multi-core.workok.bak"
    }
  ],
